<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{غَشِيَهُم}</span> ... عَلَاهُمْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَالظُّلَلِ}</span> ... كَالسَّحَابِ، أَوِ الجِبَالِ المُظِلَّةِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُّقْتَصِدٌ}</span> ... مُتَوَسِّطٌ لَمْ يَقُمْ بِشُكْرِ اللهِ عَلَى وَجْهِ الكَمَالِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَتَّارٍ}</span> ... غَدَّارٍ تَاقِضٍ لِلْعَهْدِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَفُورٍ}</span> ... جَحُودٍ لِنِعَمِ اللهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَّا يَجْزِي وَالِدٌ}</span> ... لَا يُغْنِي فِيهِ وَالِدٌ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَلَا تَغُرَّنَّكُمُ}</span> ... فَلَا تَخْدَعَنَّكُمْ، وَتُلْهِيَنَّكُمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْغَرُورُ}</span> ... مَا يَغُرُّ وَيَخْدَعُ مِنْ شَيْطَانٍ وَغَيْرِهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>